Revision history for Perl extension Mail::FilterXML.

0.1  Mon Jul 24 18:59:26 2000
	- Converted from script to module.

0.2  Tue Oct 17 15:00:51 2000
	- added filtering based on subject - ebs
	- Added action_cmd and action_params attributes to Rules - ebs
	- added mapping of Mail::Audit attributes into #var# in action_params - ebs
		#from# = Mail::Audit->from
		#to# = Mail::Audit->to
		#subject# = Mail::Audit->subject

0.3  Wed Mar 13 01:17:34 2002
	- added the ability to have multiple actions per rule. - ebs
        - minor documentation changes (mm)
